{"tid":2128422,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"悉尼中國留學生偽造自己被綁架視頻，要求中國親人支付贖金。背後原因令人動容。","createTime":"2020-07-28T03:23:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T11:45:33.000Z","uid":48040,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"440f6a997f7a731b3c3d7d4b5a9424743136835d","tid":2128422,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T03:23:14.000Z","msg":"悉尼中國留學生接到自稱「中國大使館」的電話，話佢涉及違法犯罪活動，要求支付一筆錢，否則就會被遣返。<br />\n其實呢D騙案香港都好多。但唔同的是，「中國大使館」（假冒的，除非唔係）會教呢D留學生偽造自己被綁架的視頻，然後從身處中國的父母嗰度取得「贖款」，用來支付比騙徒。所交納的贖金從2萬到30萬澳元不等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/EagleNews_HK/status/1287948583996542978?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEagleNews_HK%2Fstatus%2F1287948583996542978%3Fs%3D20&d=oFI5KSBgBGvHra6dYUznBqzbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=746befad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEagleNews_HK%2Fstatus%2F1287948583996542978%3Fs%3D20&h=3f3f3a8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/EagleNews_HK/status/1287948583996542978?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"634c1aa94359231bfcaec3c7f145e95beef4eaa7","tid":2128422,"uid":194326,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T03:24:27.000Z","msg":"對腳都綁唔實<br />\n霞姨～～～"},{"pid":"303bcbd50f1981e5e1caf7b4bced395739e88741","tid":2128422,"uid":48040,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"634c1aa94359231bfcaec3c7f145e95beef4eaa7","tid":2128422,"uid":194326,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T03:24:27.000Z","msg":"對腳都綁唔實<br />\n霞姨～～～"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T03:25:21.000Z","msg":"臨時演員，係咁上下"},{"pid":"5e85938cf4c19c95b9b5f114e3afb131531654c4","tid":2128422,"uid":117689,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T03:26:25.000Z","msg":"諗起香港人去到外國 有咩事要求支那領事館 真係喊出黎"},{"pid":"d90b1ef4f46e0a6a3615c7ff25cf6f5fcd3eec77","tid":2128422,"uid":12628,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T03:26:27.000Z","msg":"以為用咁嘅方法